This is a surveillance tool developed using raspberry pi.
This program allows start a surveillance session. The images   
captured by this client device is sent to server for further   
processing.

Start Surveillance:
This is used to start a surveillance session.

Stop:
This is used to stop a surveillance session.

Current task status:
This block information on the current activity 
is provided.

Capturing image - This means the camera of Pi is 
engaging in the image capture process.

Transferring - The captured image is being 
transmitted to the server.

Session stopped: No activity


Quit:
This is used to close the current session.

Version:1.0
